PART B — COMMERCIAL USE

For any use of the Software that falls outside the scope of
Non-Commercial Use as defined in Part A, a separate commercial license
agreement is required.

Commercial license benefits include:
  - Best-trained model weights (DIRTY 30k-sample, 113-epoch RTX 3090)
  - Docker full-stack deployment image
  - Priority email support (response within 2 business days)
  - Custom training on your observational data
  - CSST-adapted modules (available post-2027)
  - Private deployment assistance
  - Indemnification (subject to agreement terms)

Pricing is tailored to the scope of use. Typical arrangements:
  - Single-seat academic-commercial hybrid: ¥3,000–8,000/year
  - Small team (≤5 users): ¥15,000–30,000/year
  - Institutional / enterprise: custom quote
  - Perpetual source-code license: custom quote

To obtain a commercial license, contact:
  Email: cometh@proton.me
  Subject: COMETH Commercial License Inquiry

Please include:
  (1) Your name and affiliation
  (2) Brief description of intended use
  (3) Number of users / deployment scale
  (4) Budget range or expected license type

